Specs

Trezor Safe 5

Trezor Safe 5 is designed to be the ultimate hardware wallet for bitcoin users who prioritize both security and user-friendliness. With its vibrant color touchscreen and tactile feedback features from the Trezor Touch haptic engine, it offers an intuitive experience that’s easy to navigate.

Based on a decade of open-source security and privacy development, the Trezor Safe 5 provides a reliable foundation for safeguarding your bitcoin. It employs the NDA-free EAL 6+ Secure Element along with PIN and passphrase protection, ensuring strong defense against both online and offline threats. The addition of an enhanced 20-word wallet backup standard allows for a seamless transition from a Standard Single-share Backup to an Advanced Multi-share Backup, enhancing wallet recovery protection with added security measures.

The Trezor Safe 5 seamlessly integrates with the complete Trezor ecosystem, which includes user-friendly desktop and mobile apps. This integration simplifies tasks including sending, receiving, buying, and selling. Additionally, users have access to a wide array of third-party services, enabling them to tailor their bitcoin experience to their individual preferences and requirements.

Whether you’re new to hardware wallets or an experienced bitcoin user, the Trezor Safe 5 offers unparalleled security and convenience for storing, managing, and using your bitcoin.

Frequently asked questions

Why should I use a Bitcoin-only hardware wallet?

Go for the Trezor Safe 5 Bitcoin-only hardware wallet for the ultimate Bitcoin experience! Specifically designed for Bitcoin OGs, whales, and enthusiasts, this hardware wallet ensures a seamless journey with specialized operations and features to manage all your Bitcoin accounts and balances.

Is a Bitcoin-only hardware wallet more secure?

Both editions of the Trezor Safe 5 provide exceptional security with their built-in Secure Element layer. Elevate your bitcoin protection to new heights by pairing the Trezor Safe 5 Bitcoin-only hardware wallet with a passphrase. Step confidently into the future of bitcoin security, backed by the industry pioneers.

What's the difference between Bitcoin-only Trezor Safe 5 and universal Trezor Safe 5?

The Trezor Safe 5 Bitcoin-only hardware wallet is purpose-built for Bitcoin-only transactions, ensuring a seamless experience with all functions and features optimized for managing Bitcoin accounts and transactions efficiently. Meanwhile, the versatile Trezor Safe 5 universal hardware wallet accommodates not only Bitcoin transactions but also supports 1000s of other coins and tokens.

Why should I use Trezor Safe 5 Bitcoin-only wallet instead of having bitcoin on an online exchange?

Storing your bitcoin online? Risky move, my friend. Those online exchanges? Hacker magnets. Always trying to break in and cause chaos. But hey, behold the Trezor Safe 5 Bitcoin-only hardware wallet! It's your bitcoin fortress—offline and super secure. Your bitcoin safe and sound.
